-- Remove the Communities feature (full teardown): Posts/Feed, Pools, Help
-- Requests, Leadership (head applications), Ads, Discount claims, and the
-- community-scoped fields on Opportunity/Resource/Chat/Report/Complaint/Review.
--
-- Data-safety notes (hand-inserted, NOT auto-generated by `prisma migrate diff`):
--   1. Historical COMMUNITY_MANAGERS reviews become meaningless without their
--      community context, so they are deleted before reviews.communityId drops.
--   2. COMMUNITY-type chats have no title of their own today; backfill the
--      title from the community name before chats.communityId drops, so they
--      don't render as unnamed chats afterward (see messaging.service.ts's
--      listMyChats() title fallback: `chat.title ?? other?.profile?.fullName
--      ?? 'Group chat'`).

